{
  "stem": "22047.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- I-- I guess I-- I thought that, well, it's something different than-- than what I expected then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I'd had no idea going into this camp what I was going to see, nor did my guys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of us-- I didn't get sick enough to vomit, but I got sick to my stomach, of course.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a number of them just threw up, seeing this horrific situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I-- this Belgian officer and some of the other people that-- that were actually quartered in-- near this entrance that we went through, they weren't in the main barracks with the rest of the internees.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were treated a little more humanely, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I guess so, because he was-- he was not emaciated like the other-- most of the other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took me into some of the barracks to show-- show me what-- what it was like in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just awful, just awful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the looked like cordwood, bodies lying around the camp everywhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Went to the crematorium, and it was stacked to the ceiling with bodies that hadn't been cremated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's stop here for a minute, because I want you to describe this whole scene on the next tape.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to change tapes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
